<h4 id="transactions--reduction-key" sourcefile="articles/supply-chain/master-planning/planning-optimization/demand-forecast.md" sourcestartlinenumber="143">Transactions – reduction key</h4>
<p sourcefile="articles/supply-chain/master-planning/planning-optimization/demand-forecast.md" sourcestartlinenumber="145">If you select <strong sourcefile="articles/supply-chain/master-planning/planning-optimization/demand-forecast.md" sourcestartlinenumber="145">Transactions - reduction key</strong>, the forecast requirements are reduced by the transactions that occur during the periods that are defined by the reduction key.</p>
