<td sourcefile="articles/supply-chain/master-planning/planning-optimization/demand-forecast.md" sourcestartlinenumber="244">December 15 in the previous year</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/supply-chain/master-planning/planning-optimization/demand-forecast.md" sourcestartlinenumber="244">500</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/supply-chain/master-planning/planning-optimization/demand-forecast.md" sourcestartlinenumber="244">Sales order requirements</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/supply-chain/master-planning/planning-optimization/demand-forecast.md" sourcestartlinenumber="245">
