<td sourcefile="articles/supply-chain/master-planning/planning-optimization/demand-forecast.md" sourcestartlinenumber="248">1,000</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/supply-chain/master-planning/planning-optimization/demand-forecast.md" sourcestartlinenumber="248">Forecast requirements period January 12 to end</td>
